insert  into `templatable_partial_field`(`id`,`templatable_partial_id`,`name`,`type`,`value`,`created_at`,`updated_at`,`deleted_at`,`key`,`container_attributes`) values (1,1,'content','','<p>Sysflow&trade; Base is the core hub that your complete business management solution runs from. It uses&nbsp;bolt-on, mix and match modules and allows you to manage everything from your website to job&nbsp;quotes,&nbsp;offsite projects&nbsp;to HR, vehicle maintenance to payroll - all&nbsp;in one central&nbsp;place.</p><p>Sysflow&nbsp;is designed for staggered deployment at a rate that suits your business, to minimise business disruption and allow staff time to learn one new system before introducing further developments.</p><p>Security and essential fix updates are automatically deployed to the base platform modules as soon as they become available, to ensure that your system is as secure as possible at all times.</p><p>      </p><p>Sysflow&trade; Base consists of a number of core modules which provides an initial level of functionality, from which you can then build upon.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><a href=\"/roles-module\">Roles</a> - define the level of access by individual,&nbsp;seniority, department or a custom combination choice</li><li><a href=\"/users-module\">Users</a> - assign each employee pre-defined permissions</li><li><a href=\"/styling-module\">Styling</a> - a&nbsp;developer tool to apply branding elements to your system</li><li><a href=\"/contact-manager-module\">Contact Manager</a> - manage customers, suppliers and internal customer profiles</li></ul>','2014-12-24 14:01:20','2014-12-24 14:01:20',NULL,'',''),(2,2,'content','','<p>\r\n	We recognise that every business is&nbsp;different and one size does not fit all. Our packages are designed to be&nbsp;flexible to suit your specific&nbsp;business&nbsp;needs and&nbsp;range from standard websites through to complete workflow platforms.&nbsp;</p><p>Our website content management system (CMS) is designed specifically for&nbsp;use by non-developers, so its easy for everyone to use and absolutely&nbsp;no coding knowledge&nbsp;is necessary.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sysflow Standard Website</strong></p><p>Entry level website with a&nbsp;selection of&nbsp;website modules (such as Pages and Contact Form) which is easily&nbsp;administered through the CMS.</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\">Hybrid&nbsp;CMS</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>A combination package, facilitating&nbsp;business workflow (with&nbsp;modules  such as Tasks or Jobs)&nbsp;together with&nbsp;your public-facing&nbsp;website.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Sell products online and accept online payments from all major providers</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Business Software Application\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Quote Engines\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Project Management Software\r\n</p>','2014-12-24 14:01:56','2014-12-24 14:01:56',NULL,'',''),(3,3,'content','','<p>We are currently developing a number of different modules&nbsp;</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:17','2014-12-24 14:02:17',NULL,'',''),(4,4,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:36','2014-12-24 14:02:36',NULL,'',''),(5,5,'content','','<p>Sysflow Base is the foundation on which each website is built and provides the robust framework for deployment and update of any number of modules. </p><p>  </p><p>Based on a monthly subscription model, Sysflow Base includes a number of core modules, together with security and development upgrades and hosting on our secure servers. &nbsp;</p>','2014-12-24 14:02:54','2014-12-24 14:02:54',NULL,'',''),(6,6,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:11','2014-12-24 14:03:11',NULL,'',''),(7,7,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:40','2014-12-24 14:03:40',NULL,'',''),(8,8,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:03:51','2014-12-24 14:03:51',NULL,'',''),(9,9,'content','','<p>Sysflow helped us when we were finding it hard to find the time to complete our own website internally. They quickly picked up the designs and ideas we had and built our site with real speed, efficiency and professionalism.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','2014-12-24 14:04:05','2014-12-24 14:04:05',NULL,'',''),(10,10,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:04:25','2014-12-24 14:04:25',NULL,'',''),(11,11,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:04:34','2014-12-24 14:04:34',NULL,'',''),(12,12,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:04:45','2014-12-24 14:04:45',NULL,'',''),(13,13,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:04:57','2014-12-24 14:04:57',NULL,'',''),(14,14,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:05:08','2014-12-24 14:05:08',NULL,'',''),(15,15,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:05:24','2014-12-24 14:05:24',NULL,'',''),(16,16,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:05:36','2014-12-24 14:05:36',NULL,'',''),(17,17,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:05:45','2014-12-24 14:05:45',NULL,'',''),(18,18,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:05:55','2014-12-24 14:05:55',NULL,'',''),(19,19,'content','','<p>\r\n	Get in touch using the contact details below:\r\n</p>','2014-12-24 14:06:25','2014-12-24 14:06:25',NULL,'',''),(20,20,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:06:46','2014-12-24 14:06:46',NULL,'',''),(21,21,'content','','<p>Coming soon</p>','2014-12-24 14:06:54','2014-12-24 14:06:54',NULL,'',''),(22,22,'content','','<p>One of our four core&nbsp;<a href=\"/sysflow-platform\">Sysflow Platform</a> modules, Contact Manager allows you to centralise&nbsp;all of&nbsp;your contacts and categorise according to your business need. For example, they could be:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Customers</li><li>Suppliers</li><li>Business Lead</li><li>Internal Customer</li><li>Custom label of your choice</li></ul><p>Maintain a database of information and search or&nbsp;filter&nbsp;by Company, Contact, Product and more. Being held centrally, it ensures that there is no duplication and&nbsp;all contact information is kept fully up to date as it is changed in one place only.</p>','2014-12-24 14:07:41','2014-12-24 14:07:41',NULL,'',''),(23,23,'content','','<p>One of the four core modules which forms part of our&nbsp;<a href=\"/sysflow-platform\">Sysflow Base platform</a>, Users allows you to create individual profiles for employees and,&nbsp;in conjunction with the&nbsp;<a href=\"/roles-module\">Roles Module</a>, allows you to assign specific roles and permissions at granular level by:</p><ul><li>Individual</li><li>Seniority</li><li>Department&nbsp;</li><li>Or a custom combination of your choice</li></ul><p><strong>Applications</strong></p><p>Used&nbsp;by Management to define which employees,&nbsp;external&nbsp;contractors or Departments&nbsp;are able to&nbsp;access specific parts of a system and at what level.</p><p></p>','2014-12-24 14:08:28','2014-12-24 14:08:28',NULL,'',''),(24,24,'content','','<p>One of the&nbsp;four core Sysflow Base modules, Styling is a module for developers which allows the look and feel of the platform to be customised and&nbsp;branded&nbsp;according to your exact specification.</p>','2014-12-24 14:08:49','2014-12-24 14:08:49',NULL,'',''),(25,25,'content','','<p>One of the four core modules which make up&nbsp;<a href=\"http://sysflow-platform\">Sysflow Base platform</a>, Roles allows you to define the level of accessibility an&nbsp;employee or contractor has to a system by:</p><ul><li>Individual&nbsp;</li><li>Seniority</li><li>Department&nbsp;</li><li>Custom combination of your choosing</li></ul><p>Used in collaboration with the&nbsp;<a href=\"/users-module\">Users Module</a> you are able&nbsp;to allocate these permissions at individual&nbsp;Employee level.</p><p></p>','2014-12-24 14:09:20','2014-12-24 14:09:20',NULL,'',''),(26,26,'content','','<p>Quickly create or edit&nbsp;pages on&nbsp;your website and add,&nbsp;edit or&nbsp;delete copy, images and more using our easy to use interface.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Related Modules</strong></p><p>In conjunction with our&nbsp;<a href=\"#\">Blocks</a> module, you can customise the layout of a page by&nbsp;inserting additional&nbsp;types of content such as images, buttons, text or forms by dragging and dropping design elements into the page.</p><p><a href=\"/menu-module\">Menu Module</a> allows you to easily&nbsp;assign a&nbsp;page or pages&nbsp;to a navigation bar or channel&nbsp;the way people move through your site to different areas</p><p>Using pages&nbsp;alongside our&nbsp;<a href=\"/seo-pages-module\">SEO Pages Module</a>, you can&nbsp;optimise your on-page content to target the most relevant keywords for your business.</p>','2014-12-24 14:09:56','2014-12-24 14:09:56',NULL,'',''),(27,27,'content','','<p>This module works closely with our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages-module\">Pages Module</a> and allows you to design the navigational elements on your website.</p><p>Define which pages will appear and where&nbsp;they will be displayed within each menu bar.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Typical Application</strong></p><ul><li>\"Nest\" a number of related product&nbsp;pages under an overarching category page</li><li>Choose which of your main products appear on your main navigation bar and which secondary products appear in the left hand navigation</li></ul>','2014-12-24 14:10:12','2014-12-24 14:10:12',NULL,'',''),(28,28,'content','','<p>This module works directly with our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sysflow.co.uk/pages-module\">Pages Module</a> and allows you to optimise your existing&nbsp;website page content and meta information (URL,&nbsp;Title & Description) to increase your website\'s&nbsp;visibility and rankings&nbsp;in search engines results&nbsp;such as Google, Bing and Yahoo. Customise page-specific information to target the best keywords for your business.</p><p>Preview how your page will appear in Google search results&nbsp;listings and how your title and descriptions will be displayed to visitors.</p><p></p><p></p>','2014-12-24 14:10:31','2014-12-24 14:10:31',NULL,'',''),(29,29,'content','','<p>Products info</p>','2014-12-24 14:10:50','